    "13": {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "# Active Active Dashboard\n\nThe active Active Dashboard is responsible for displaying key metrics for Redis Enterprise Active Active deployments. An Active Active deployment is when two databases in two  distinct clusters (usually) in different regions are synchronizing with each other using CRDT"
    },
